                "type": "element",
                "tag": "em",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Distant kin of giant owls from the Feywild, owlin come in many shapes and sizes, from petite and fluffy to wide-winged and majestic. Owlin have arms and legs like other Humanoids, as well as wings that extend from their back and shoulders."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "br",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Like owls, owlin are graced with feathers that make no sound when they move or fly, making it easy for them to sneak up on you in the library."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "br",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Your owlin character might be nocturnal. Or perhaps your character is simply prone to rise later, embodying the common nickname of night owl."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
